                  </persName> were indicted for<rs id="t18430130-650-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18430130-650-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18430130-650-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>stealing, on the <rs id="t18430130-cd-59" type="crimeDate">
